Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祝福你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為你自己所做的事感到榮耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱撒？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別淘氣 凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小良？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美菜 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 良介
Comment: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.17,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}深く激しく そっと優しく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.40,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}突き動かして、情熱に訴えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.90,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}ひとつになろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:30.22,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}泳いだ目線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:33.46,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}不埒な彷徨えるエゴイズム
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.94,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}着飾った秘密のベール
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:38.86,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}脱がせてくれるのはあなた?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:42.10,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}露骨に躍った慾望 それは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.46,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}私のドコが理由なの?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.85,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}私のナニに昂っているの?ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.51,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}待って…少し妬けるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.34,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}空より遠い 冥より深い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:01.61,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}闇の城より舞い降りしFreaky Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.71,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Death sickleが指揮者ね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:08.26,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}魅惑のレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.90,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}突き刺さる心の十字架に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.51,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}何を誓って戯れようか?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.59,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}焦らした指先
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.41,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}先駆けた誘惑の雫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.44,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}糸を手繰って すぐココに来て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.31,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}心から溢れ出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.37,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}甘い蜜に愛を這わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.66,OP-JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Reason why Kiss 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.17,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}深深的激動 輕輕的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:19.40,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}付諸於動作 狂熱地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.90,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}互相合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:30.22,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}飄遊不定的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:33.46,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}下流隨便的自我主義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:35.94,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}這張戴上秘密的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.06,0:01:38.86,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}讓我卸下心防的人是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:42.10,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}這份明顯雀躍的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:44.46,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}就是我身在此處的理由嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.85,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}到底在對我興奮些什麼呢？你說說看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:50.51,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}等下…我有點吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:56.34,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}比天空更高遠 比冥府更深遂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:01.61,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}來自黑暗城堡的降臨者Freaky Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.71,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Death sickle是指揮者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:08.26,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}曲名是魅惑的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.90,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}對著刺穿心臟的十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.51,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}要宣誓什麼來玩耍好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:17.59,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}焦急的指尖上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.41,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}有顆先發制人的迷人水滴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.44,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}操弄著細線 即將在此處出現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:26.31,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}從心中奔放而出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:29.37,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}用膩甜的蜜汁沾滿愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:34.66,OP-CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)}{\blur2.5}Reason why Kiss 不要離開我
